data.description: The home is a timeless well-built custom home.  The home has quality unique custom features and many upgrades. The previous owner who built the home spared no expense when this home was built. There is storage space everywhere and a place for everything. Solid stained wood doors, stained glass windows, sub zero fridge and freezer and spacious walk in pantry.  Unfinished basement is 623 sq ft and 1613 sq ft garage/shop (2 car and separate shop with 3 car).  2x6 framed construction, patio w/built in barbeque and bar, spanish courtyard with fountain and benches. Beautifully landscaped w/14 pomegranate trees, 2 pecan, 2 fig, a lemon and a pomelo tree.  RV gate and plenty of parking.
